{"tid":1766480,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港人十一奉獻]月付贊助網媒/抗爭基金/民調機構 推動公民社會發展","createTime":"2019-12-02T15:12:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-07T02:06:31.000Z","uid":206090,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3bd642b6eceb6cf4c7c6ca09945edfb9613f780c","tid":1766480,"uid":206090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:12:05.000Z","msg":"每月將人工既十份之一 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，分別贊助比支持公民社會、支持抗爭運動的各個機構組織，以便推動公民社會發展及支援有需要被捕人士 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。而且生活上盡量選擇黃色經濟圈的店舖。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">年尾就尼出雙糧，不如再捐多份呀~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n有咩機構組織介紹？不如下面一人介紹一個，等大家自己簡。我講先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n---------------<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港民意研究所</span> ，由鍾庭耀博士於一九九一年成立，前身是香港大學民意研究計劃。提供高質素的調查服務，進行了獨立調查和其他類型的研究。<br />\n捐款: <a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/donation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fdonation&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRVcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=a7d51189\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/donation</a><br />\n訂閱: 最低每月$100HKD，就可以成為普通會員 <a href=\"https://www.pori.hk/subscription\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pori.hk%2Fsubscription&d=r4%2BjDf%2BCRrsm4RwUuvkwRVcETUAZGKrTpJw0Ojiq68w%3D&h=194fdeb4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.pori.hk/subscription</a><br />\n支付方式: 信用卡（經網上系統支付）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xhFtse5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxhFtse5.jpg&h=8f7a8490&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">您地都介紹下有咩機構值得贊助啦！！</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"38071a72638673ffa9ff03ae651847b5ed760c0c","tid":1766480,"uid":24926